item.title: About me
item.description: Who am I? Hi there! I’m Dr. Bikki Subedi , an enthusiastic doctor from Jhapa, here on a journey to serve people to make and aspire them to stay healthy! I have completed my M.B.B.S degree on year 2022 A.D from a prestigious University (R.U) in Bangladesh. I have completed my internship training for a span of 12 months. I am currently working in multiple hospitals across Kathmandu Valley in a pursuit to learn more and heal more.
